T02D3060:116a-1: a'arya aa tsa la kro dha r'a dza sto tra /
T02D3060:116a-3: khro bo'i rgyal po 'phags pa mi g-yo ba la bstod pa /
T02D3060:116a-4: khro bo'i rgyal po mi g-yo ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3060:116a-5: mi g-yo zhes bya'i khro bo ni //
T02D3060:116a-6: ral gri zhags pa legs par thogs //
T02D3060:116a-7: spyi bo'i zur phung g-yon du 'khyil //
T02D3060:116a-9: klu chen la sogs thams cad kyi //
T02D3060:116a-10: rgyan rnams kun gyis rab tu brgyan //
T02D3060:116a-11: byis pa'i gzugs can 'gying bag can //
T02D3060:116a-12: rdo rje'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3060:116a-13: dpal ldan nang na thugs rje'i rang bzhin can //
T02D3060:116a-14: gdug pa 'dul phyir phyi rol khro tshul ston //
T02D3060:116a-15: chos nyid mi 'gyur sku mdog mthing nag zhal //
T02D3060:116a-16: bcom ldan mi g-yo mgon la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3060:116a-17: thugs rje'i dbyings nas bzhengs pa'i sku mchog ni //
T02D3060:116a-18: ye shes me dpung 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
T02D3060:116a-19: sna tshogs padma nyi ma'i gdan la bzhugs //
T02D3060:116a-20: zhal gcig phyag gnyis mthing nag rngam pa'i sku //
T02D3060:116a-21: zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum bgegs chen du ma gzir //
T02D3060:116a-22: stag dang sprul gyi rgyan gyis rnam par brgyan //
T02D3060:116b-0: lha dang @116b lha min skrag mdzad phyag g-yas na //
T02D3060:116b-1: shes rab ral gri 'bar ba 'debs pa'i tshul //
T02D3060:116b-2: 'byung po skrag mdzad phyag g-yon sdigs mdzub ste //
T02D3060:116b-3: thugs rjes lus can mi gtor rdo rje zhags //
T02D3060:116b-4: skye shi rtsad gcod rno dkar mche ba gcigs //
T02D3060:116b-5: spyan gnyis dmar zlum thugs rjes phyogs bcur gzigs ;
T02D3060:116b-6: / thugs rjes khros pas dbu skra gyen du 'khyil //
T02D3060:116b-7: mi bskyod la sogs rigs lngas dbul brgyan //
T02D3060:116b-8: ma rungs 'dul zhing 'gro don rdzogs mdzad pa'i //
T02D3060:116b-9: sprul pa'i khro rgyal sna tshogs sku las 'phro //
T02D3060:116b-10: 'gro bkun gyi sdug bsngal zhi mdzad cing //
T02D3060:116b-11: bde bdag la rim gyis mgon mdzad pa //
T02D3060:116b-12: 'gro ba'i mgon po shin tu thugs rje can //
T02D3060:116b-13: khyod nyid dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad lags //
T02D3060:116b-14: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad khyod lags pas //
T02D3060:116b-15: khro rgyal ye shes sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D3060:116b-16: 'jigs byed drag po'i gsung la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D3060:116b-17: gnyis med rtse gcig thugs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D3060:116b-18: bdag kyang khyod ltar 'gro don bgyi slad du //
T02D3060:116b-19: rtse gcig sems kyis khyod bsgom gsang sngags bzlas //
T02D3060:116b-20: dus rnams rtag tu khro rgyal khyod bsten na //
T02D3060:116b-21: thugs rje chen pos byin gyis brlabs mdzad de //
T02D3060:116b-22: ye shes sku mchog mngon sum stsal nas kyang ;
T02D3060:116b-23: / sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bdag la stsol //
T02D3060:116b-24: sgrub la bar chad byed pa'i bdud dgra rnams //
T02D3060:116b-25: pha rol 'joms pa'i stobs kyis med par mdzod //
T02D3060:116b-26: dus 'di nas bzung byang chub snying po'i bar //
T02D3060:116b-27: lha mchog khyod la bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
T02D3060:116b-28: dus rnams rtag tu khyod kyis bsrung du gsol //
T02D3060:116b-29: khro bo'i rgyal po mi g-yo ba la bstod pa /
T02D3060:116b-30: pandi ta d'i pam ka ra shr'i dzny'a nas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
